messages.messageBody:
Meghan:

You can always order for BBC America on-line. They have a British store.
We have one in Tucson called the Tudor Rose. I paid $2.75 per Pork Pie the
other day, but it was delicious. Also paid $1.75 for what looks like
Sainsbury's Sausage Rolls. Again delicious so well worth it... By the way
I'm born and bred in England until age 21 and now for 21 years have lived in
the US. I'm a US and British Citizen so I get the best of both worlds.

Dawn
